WORKING STABLE SETUP

# Terminal 1
gz sim -v4 ~/ardupilot_gazebo/worlds/iris_runway.sdf            (play + click iris_with_gimbal and follow)     #if u get "link 1 down" in console, meaning u didn't play/run the simulation
  # Terminal 2
cd ~/ardupilot/ArduCopter
sim_vehicle.py -v ArduCopter -f JSON --console --map

    # AFTER THE CONSOLE OPENS, UNDER STABILIZE>             (only in the start necessary)
param set FRAME_CLASS 1
param set FRAME_TYPE 0

# In MAVProxy
STABiLIZE> mode guided
STABiLIZE> mode
GUIDED> GUIDED     #shows automatically
GUIDED> arm throttle
GUIDED> takeoff 5      # 5m up the altitude

      # velocity commands
      GUIDED> guided X Y Z
            X = forward/back
            Y = left/right
            Z = altitude
  Ex: GUIDED> guided 10 0 5
  meaning: move 10m forward
           no sideways shift
           stay at 5m altitude

